Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.32,0:01:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筱田步美\N最近我跟朋友浅野一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.52,0:01:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沉迷于通过自创的舞蹈\N挥洒一身的汗来瘦身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.36,0:01:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太太 你的私处露出来了哟!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.24,0:01:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你\N谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.48,0:01:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的舞蹈有点难呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.76,0:01:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这个肯定可以瘦身的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.48,0:01:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的呢\N我瘦了好多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.92,0:02:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过跳舞是非常不错的兴趣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.80,0:02:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过这也能瘦身\N腿也能瘦下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.32,0:02:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你丈夫肯定也非常开心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.48,0:02:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定会的\N你丈夫肯定会开心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.44,0:02:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我丈夫半年才回来一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.52,0:02:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了\N我们休息一下又关始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.76,0:02:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.36,0:02:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天到此结束吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.28,0:03:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的呢\N下周继续绾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.52,0:03:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了\N下周到我家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.68,0:03:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是没问题呀 可是你丈夫\N不是在家吗？ 这样不好吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.04,0:03:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个没没问题\N总是我过来打扰你家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.00,0:03:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样呀 一直让你过来 真是抱歉了\N那下周就过去浅野家里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.80,0:03:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样呀\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.04,0:03:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 跳舞是跳舞\N上次你丢失的钱包 找到了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.80,0:03:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.52,0:03:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面并没有多少钱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.56,0:03:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能不能认真一点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.36,0:03:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.88,0:03:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开始跳舞之后\N有没有比刚结婚的时候要瘦呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.40,0:04:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.20,0:04:06.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.96,0:04:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公 我们生一个小孩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.32,0:04:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.28,0:04:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人吗\N来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.96,0:04:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午安 欢迎你\N午安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.68,0:04:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起呀 在你们\N休息的时候过来打扰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.04,0:04:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.96,0:05:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.64,0:05:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你进来吧\N打扰了 请进吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.28,0:05:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了\N进来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.12,0:06:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 要不要试试那个呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.00,0:06:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就试试看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.24,0:06:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样的 就是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.80,0:06:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做得好吗?\N做得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.32,0:06:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不错呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.24,0:06:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺舒服的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.32,0:06:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还可以继续转圈吗?\N继续吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.72,0:06:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续转圈呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.04,0:09:23.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公 你怎么啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.48,0:09:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我端茶过来了\N谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.52,0:09:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我放到那边去了\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.44,0:09:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.44,0:09:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就继续吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.84,0:10:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉非常有效呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.36,0:10:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天谢谢你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.48,0:10:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经练得很上手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.52,0:10:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 下个周末\N你有空吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.68,0:10:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.28,0:10:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞路马上完成了\N我跟步美想给你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.52,0:11:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以呀\N真的吗？ 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.72,0:11:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就下周了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.48,0:11:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安\N晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.84,0:11:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 我们来制这孩子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.48,0:11:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉呀\N今天劳烦你们过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.08,0:11:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公\N你好好看看我们练习的成果哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.48,0:12:17.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 我明白了\N我马上过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.00,0:12:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N对不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.96,0:12:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦？\N上次丢失的钱包 好像找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.76,0:12:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以去颔吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.28,0:12:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没问题吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.52,0:12:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题\N那老公你看看步美的练习成果吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.52,0:12:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.44,0:12:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你注意一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.16,0:12:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个\N那你能看看我的练习成果吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.60,0:15:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.88,0:15:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到这边来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.88,0:17:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 怎么样呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.36,0:18:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常的棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.36,0:18:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.00,0:18:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的舞蹈真的好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.12,0:18:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了\N真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.04,0:18:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.40,0:18:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了\N你结婚婚很长时间了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.00,0:18:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.72,0:18:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你们感情那么好\N真是美慕呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.56,0:18:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来是这样的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.44,0:18:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像新婚一样\N保因为她把你带到我这里来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.36,0:18:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的吗？我们刚结婚的时候\N感情并没有这么好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.00,0:18:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.04,0:19:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?你怎么啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.68,0:19:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 那个 那个\N我是真的觉得太太的跳舞好棒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.12,0:19:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好厉害呢\N是真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.80,0:19:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能再跳一次给我看看吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.08,0:19:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再跳一次吗？是的\N好的 我明白了 可以吗 是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.04,0:19:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.48,0:21:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个\N你怎么了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.56,0:21:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.88,0:21:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.60,0:21:17.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以说出来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.60,0:21:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 那个 太太\N是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.56,0:21:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的私处露出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.80,0:21:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私处？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.04,0:21:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.32,0:21:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.40,0:21:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.76,0:21:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.96,0:21:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个\N是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.80,0:21:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 那个 对不起\N喂 你住手啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.60,0:21:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.52,0:21:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 因为我看到了\N你干什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.48,0:22:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你停下来\N可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.20,0:22:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.08,0:22:06.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 不可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.96,0:22:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 你是浅野太太的丈夫\N你这样做 我会被骂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.64,0:22:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做出这种事情?可是你的\N我都看到你的私处了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.88,0:22:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.40,0:22:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.92,0:22:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你住手啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.24,0:22:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.88,0:22:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.96,0:22:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等等啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.20,0:22:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害呀\N好羞耻啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.44,0:23:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羞耻?可是太太你一直都是\N这个样子在跳舞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.48,0:23:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样\N你别看啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.32,0:23:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.56,0:23:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊 好柔软
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.08,0:23:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以的 特别是这里\N这里看得很清楚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.68,0:23:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以的 这里好厉害呀\N不可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.04,0:23:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 对不起\N我并没有打算这样做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.88,0:23:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你住手啦\N我看到这之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.08,0:23:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 你在干什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.12,0:23:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法忍耐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.36,0:23:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.28,0:23:52.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害羞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.20,0:24:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那个可是太太你自己以如此\N羞耻的姿势一直在跳舞的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.60,0:24:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并没有 那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.88,0:24:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.32,0:24:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.84,0:24:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私处好柔软啊\N不可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.92,0:24:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别这样做啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.24,0:24:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面湿哒哒了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.08,0:24:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.64,0:24:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个太厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.84,0:24:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.48,0:24:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.76,0:24:52.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:54.32,0:24:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么\N私处都露出来了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:00.24,0:25:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 你停下来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:03.60,0:25:06.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你露出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.64,0:25:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:08.24,0:25:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别揉弄啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:13.84,0:25:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在摩擦啦你 停下来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:16.88,0:25:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我要怎么做呢\N我无去停下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:30.48,0:25:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:33.84,0:25:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:45.04,0:25:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:55.12,0:25:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:03.12,0:26:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:05.04,0:26:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:07.60,0:26:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以的 我很敏感的\N这里很敏感是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:14.48,0:26:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那如果我继续揉弄的话\N不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:21.20,0:26:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在跳舞的时候\N胸部也一直在晃动吧
