Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:44.72,1:15:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 那个\N今天请你回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:48.72,1:15:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:02.16,1:16:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:05.36,1:16:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就好了
